{-x}$ 的平移可得到 $f(x)$ ，则此时 $f(x)$ 单调递增, 作出图像如下图所示,\n\n第二步:\n令\n\n$$\ng(x)=f(x)-m x+\\frac{2}{3} m=0\n$$\n\n即\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_10_24_47a253f79e08acf28419g-26.jpg?height=429&width=577&top_left_y=314&top_left_x=1342","line":523}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"8afkgc","at":1771213642551}},"smart_blocks:00-知识汇总/10-试卷汇总/功底考/功底考16题1-16套.md#科目二答题示例": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.07089318,-0.0188165,0.02642059,-0.06538294,0.00645042,0.01315977,0.01005619,-0.01633421,0.03838944,0.00120053,0.02445909,-0.03438779,0.04341413,-0.00045337,0.02222286,0.03596281,-0.01533222,-0.02679263,-0.09967513,0.00307388,0.14798579,-0.03813406,-0.01373592,-0.07126766,0.03691438,0.04284665,0.00429884,-0.02612692,-0.01751176,-0.17202799,-0.00283887,0.00919166,0.01805432,0.04060292,0.04381224,-0.06627082,-0.02818642,0.05376289,-0.06243361,0.03802197,-0.01899466,0.07699975,0.05444523,-0.02746912,0.02078838,-0.03925707,-0.02916403,-0.02103163,0.02898839,-0.02805688,-0.05423813,-0.01275865,-0.02779312,0.03881038,0.03910781,-0.01116796,-0.01444907,0.05891264,0.02567401,-0.02749553,0.04708612,0.00031329,-0.21639964,0.01414864,0.04923876,-0.00621783,0.00762146,-0.03445389,0.04083652,0.06202664,-0.04196942,0.02284747,0.03384051,0.0502886,-0.01511598,-0.02491416,0.01839479,-0.00865127,-0.08479826,-0.01993061,-0.01758464,0.0609575,0.03635941,0.01334908,-0.00850221,-0.00541124,0.02619408,-0.04247018,-0.01492709,-0.0276671,-0.00443919,-0.00258755,0.00600822,0.04456426,-0.04353217,0.00135557,0.03342303,0.04501541,-0.04169904,0.09654783,-0.03723466,0.08476783,-0.03095553,-0.09962679,0.01754821,-0.06206322,-0.04102012,-0.07876304,-0.05697233,-0.038378,-0.03455044,-0.00278386,0.07444198,-0.08730196,0.00427064,-0.00071353,0.07022057,0.03714608,-0.00605184,-0.0162451,0.03960012,0.06131952,0.0202639,-0.0386246,-0.00268582,-0.05282475,0.02934874,-0.00813274,0.06216347,0.06783175,0.03854561,-0.0159535,0.03258699,